<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.4">
<l>intira ṉukkeṉ ṟāyarka ḷeṭutta veḻilviḻa vilpaḻa naṭaicey</l>
<l>mantira vitiyil pūcaṉai peṟātu maḻaipoḻin tiṭattaḷarn tāya</l>
<l>rentamō ṭiṉavā niraitaḷa rāma lemperu māṉaru ḷeṉṉa</l>
<l>vantamil varaiyāl maḻaitaṭut tāṉait tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [Indra], having not gotten the offering in observance of the mantras</l>
<l rend="indent">[as] done [in] ancient proceedings,</l>
<l>In the colorful festival which the herders undertook saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“This is for Indra,” poured forth rain,</l>
<l>When the herders, languishing, said, “Our lord, be gracious</l>
<l rend="indent">[so that] the various cow herds along with us do not languish,”</l>
<l>The one who blocked the downpour with an indestructible  mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
